com.kontakt.sdk.android.cloud.api

Class DevicesApi

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kontakt.sdk.android.cloud.api.DevicesApi

  • public class DevicesApi
extends java.lang.Object
    An abstract representation of Devices API endpoint. Provides executors that can be used to handle all device-related requests.
